attributes.additional_details:
A Code detailing reporting lines, duties, restrictions, training and the consequences of breach or opting out is common in well-managed organisations and will benefit our Monarchy by delivering: 
(a) Clear accountability; 
(b) Less suspicion of prejudice in decision making; 
(c) Less scope for confusion on eg respect for our Monarchy and the people of the UK and Commonwealth, treatment of staff, merchandising, confidentiality, conflict of interest; and 
(d) Fewer breaches which diminish us all.
